ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectOrder Adding Toxic Substances to Schedule 1 to the Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisOrder ADDING TOXIC SUBSTANCES TO SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999 - which adds Sulfuric acid (diethyl sulfate), Sulfuric acid (dimethyl sulfate); and Benzenamine (BNST) to the List of Toxic Substances in Schedule 1 of the Act.
